Author: factcheckdotorg
Content: A popular meme on Facebook falsely purports to show a photo of "Biden's Inaugural stage" being built outside the White House. The photo shows the reviewing stand for the inaugural parade at Bill Clinton's inauguration in 1993. https://t.co/vywMvz0hTW

Author: Politifact
Content:
A video of President Trump talking while a moving crew loads his belongings from the White House isn’t real, as some online have shared. It’s a satirical clip from a “Jimmy Kimmel Live” comedy segment. 

https://t.co/mwHkIgB29U

Author: snopes
Content: The footage is from the middle of the 20th century — but this video is much more recent than 1956. https://t.co/OxLLekFeAW
